OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny low cloud in the east will
OL,6,Fclear this morning. Otherwise all
OL,7,Fparts will have a dry day with plenty
OL,8,Fof warm sunshine. Locally hot in the
OL,9,Fwest.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry with
OL,12,Fsome late sunshine. Then the rest of
OL,13,Fthe night will remain dry with some
OL,14,Flow cloud and fog patches across the
OL,15,Feast.
OL,16,
OL,17,CWednesday:FAny overnight low cloud in
OL,18,Fthe east soon burning off to leave a
OL,19,Fdry and sunny day. Very warm or hot.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
