OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FStaying dry and settled with plenty of
OL,7,Fsunshine, some early low cloud in the
OL,8,Feast and Central Belt. Very warm or
OL,9,Fhot.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
